<item>
            <title>[LU-5480] e2fsprogs build failed on el5: error: #error &quot;cannot define LPF64&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5480</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While building e2fsprogs patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/11422&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/11422&lt;/a&gt; on RHEL5 distribution, it failed as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;In file included from /var/lib/jenkins/workspace/e2fsprogs-reviews/arch/x86_64/distro/el5/../usr/src/lustre-2.3.0/lustre/include/lustre/lustre_user.h:49,
                 from /var/lib/jenkins/workspace/e2fsprogs-reviews/arch/x86_64/distro/el5/../usr/src/lustre-2.3.0/lustre/include/lustre/lustreapi.h:46,
                 from ../lib/ext2fs/lfsck.h:10,
                 from unix.c:60:
/var/lib/jenkins/workspace/e2fsprogs-reviews/arch/x86_64/distro/el5/../usr/src/lustre-2.3.0/libcfs/include/libcfs/types.h:43:3: error: #error &quot;cannot define LPF64&quot;
make[3]: *** [unix.o] Error 1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://build.hpdd.intel.com/job/e2fsprogs-reviews/240/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.hpdd.intel.com/job/e2fsprogs-reviews/240/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The failure was caused by Lustre patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/11070&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/11070&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
